\s EWE MUGENZI NI WISUZUME
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ewe ncuti yanje uri ngaha wifuza gukorer’Imana isuzume ncuti kukwiriye gukorera Imana Yera.\bd*
\p \bd Ebu ndugu yangu uko hapa watamani kutumikia Bwana jichunguze kama unapendeza kutumikia Bwana Mungu.\bd*
\b 
\pc \bdit E’ Mugenzi niwisuzume k’ukwiriye gukorera Imana Yera ihoraho E’\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit Mugenzi niwisuzume.\bdit*
\pc \bdit Ebu (ndu\bdit*\bdit gu) ujichunguze kama unaendelea \bdit*\bdit kutumikia Baba mwema Ebu ndugu ujichunguze.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd E’mugenzi wanje wisuzume har’aho woba uri impumyi canke woba uri n’ubumuga! Mbega wokorer’Imana ute?\bd*
\p \bd Ebu ndugu yangu jichunguze usije kuwa kipofu wala kuwa na ulema ndugu utatumikiya Mungu je?\bd*
\b 
\pc \bdit E’ Mugenzi niwisuzume k’ukwiriye gukorera Imana Yera ihoraho E’\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit Mugenzi niwisuzume.\bdit*
\pc \bdit Ebu (ndugu) ujichunguze kama unaendelea kutumikia Baba mwema Ebu ndugu ujichunguze.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Imana Yera ico yifuza n’uko twoyikorera n’imitima ihumuye cane yuzuye ukwicisha bugufi.\bd*
\p \bd Bwana Yesu ambacho anatamani sisi tumutumikie na roho zijaazo upole zijaazo unyenyekevu.\bd*
\b 
\pc \bdit E’ Mugenzi niwisuzume k’ukwiriye gukorera Imana Yera ihoraho E’\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit Mugenzi niwisuzume.\bdit*
